SA Explorer
  To set up:
    Connect serial port
    Open Hyperterminal, use 57600 bps, 8 data bit, none parity,
                            1 stop bit, none flow control 
    Power cycle STB
    Press Vol- button until you see a rolling LED
    Type "tvtest" on PTV> prompt
    Select 7 for Manual Menu
    Select 3 for Tune Frequency
    Select 6 for Play MPEG
    (You may need to disconnect and then connect on hyperterminal to see
